Conclusion

  1. With the above analysis we can get the information of the category who are eligible to get loan easily.
  2. As per analysis we can say that working womens are more eligible to get loan.
  3. We have Column called Target which has the 0 and 1 value for the people who faced value is for people who face difficulty paying the loan and is all other cases like the people who paid the loans even having difficulties they paid the loan amount back to back
  4. Target0 shows a dominance of females (F) compared to males (M), indicating a gender imbalance risk on other hand Target1 has a more balanced gender distribution, reducing potential gender bias.
